==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wrongdoer
<hw>Wrong"do`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who injures another, or who does wrong.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>One who commits a tort or trespass;
a trespasser; a tort feasor.</def> <rj><au>Ayliffe.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wrongdoing</ent>⟦br⟧
